## Acceptance Criteria (enhanced)

- [ ] `activation_hook` registers both `DAILY_ACCRUAL` and `MATURITY_EVENT` scheduled events
- [ ] `activation_hook` rejects activation if `maturity_date` <= `effective_datetime.date()`
- [ ] `pre_posting_hook` accepts exactly one credit posting when DEFAULT balance is zero
- [ ] `pre_posting_hook` rejects a second deposit (`AGAINST_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS`)
- [ ] `pre_posting_hook` rejects any debit/withdrawal before maturity (`AGAINST_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS`)
- [ ] `pre_posting_hook` rejects postings in a denomination other than the configured one (`WRONG_DENOMINATION`)
- [ ] `DAILY_ACCRUAL` event correctly computes `principal × (annual_rate / 365)` using `Decimal` + `ROUND_HALF_UP`
- [ ] `DAILY_ACCRUAL` posts to `ACCRUED_INTEREST` address with a `CustomInstruction` (no `client_transaction_id`)
- [ ] `DAILY_ACCRUAL` is a no-op if the DEFAULT balance is zero
- [ ] `MATURITY_EVENT` sweeps `ACCRUED_INTEREST` → `DEFAULT` in a single instruction
- [ ] `derived_parameter_hook` returns `accrued_interest` and `days_to_maturity` correctly
- [ ] Early closure path: if `allow_early_closure = true`, penalty reduces accrued interest; floor is `Decimal("0")`
- [ ] All balance reads use `BalanceCoordinate` with `Phase.COMMITTED` on the key (not the value)
- [ ] All datetimes use `ZoneInfo("UTC")` — never `timezone.utc`
- [ ] No stdlib imports in contract file
- [ ] No mutable global state
- [ ] `os-vault-test` — all tests green
- [ ] `os-vault-test --coverage` — >= 90%

---

## Unit Test Cases

Minimum 22 tests across these categories:

### Activation
1. `test_activation_valid_future_maturity` — activation succeeds, both events scheduled
2. `test_activation_rejects_maturity_today` — maturity_date == today → rejected
3. `test_activation_rejects_maturity_past` — maturity_date in the past → rejected

### Pre-Posting — Deposits
4. `test_initial_deposit_accepted` — first credit on empty account passes
5. `test_second_deposit_rejected` — second credit after funded account → `AGAINST_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS`
6. `test_wrong_denomination_rejected` — posting in USD when account is GBP → `WRONG_DENOMINATION`

### Pre-Posting — Withdrawals
7. `test_withdrawal_before_maturity_rejected` — debit → `AGAINST_TERMS_AND_CONDITIONS`
8. `test_zero_amount_posting_accepted` — edge case: zero-value posting passes

### Daily Accrual
9. `test_daily_accrual_standard_rate` — 5% AER on £1000 = £0.14/day (rounded)
10. `test_daily_accrual_zero_rate` — 0% rate produces zero accrual instruction
11. `test_daily_accrual_zero_balance` — no posting generated when principal is zero
12. `test_daily_accrual_leap_year` — 5% AER on Feb 29 still divides by 365 (not 366)
13. `test_daily_accrual_uses_decimal_precision` — result is quantized to 2 d.p. `ROUND_HALF_UP`

### Maturity Disbursement
14. `test_maturity_event_sweeps_accrued_interest` — ACCRUED_INTEREST balance moved to DEFAULT
15. `test_maturity_event_zero_interest` — no CustomInstruction when accrued = 0
16. `test_maturity_payout_correct_total` — principal + accrued in DEFAULT after event

### Early Closure
17. `test_early_closure_disabled_rejects_withdrawal` — allow_early_closure=false, debit rejected
18. `test_early_closure_enabled_applies_penalty` — penalty_rate=0.20 reduces 20% of interest
19. `test_early_closure_penalty_floor_zero` — penalty cannot make payout negative

### Derived Parameters
20. `test_derived_accrued_interest_matches_balance` — matches ACCRUED_INTEREST balance
21. `test_derived_days_to_maturity_correct` — returns correct days from today
22. `test_derived_days_to_maturity_at_maturity` — returns 0 on maturity date

---

## Non-Functional Requirements

| Concern | Requirement |
|---|---|
| Precision | All monetary calculations use `Decimal` + `ROUND_HALF_UP`. Never `float`. |
| Sandbox compliance | No `import os/sys/json/datetime/math`. Only `contracts_api` and `decimal`. |
| Immutability | No mutable module-level state. All state via Vault balance/parameter APIs. |
| Idempotency | `DAILY_ACCRUAL` is safe to re-run: checks balance before posting. |
| Denomination safety | All postings validated against configured denomination before processing. |
| API version | `api = "4.0.0"` — all patterns must be API 4.0 compliant. |
| Test coverage | `os-vault-test --coverage` must report >= 90% before opening a PR. |

---

